	<idx>exiting Image Viewer<sort>exiting image viewer<\idx>
	<idx>quitting Image Viewer<sort>quitting image viewer<\idx>
	<idx>closing Image Viewer<sort>closing image viewer<\idx>

<list bullet>
<item>Choose Exit from the File menu.
<\list>

<newline> &empty;

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet>
