<s1 id=ToMoveImageWithinViewWindowTA>To Move the Image within the View Window
	<idx>moving, image within View window<\idx>
	<idx>panning, image within View window<\idx>
	<idx>images, moving within View window<\idx>
	<idx>images, panning within View window<\idx>

<p>To move the image or page within the View window:
<list order>
<item>Click the Pan tool in the palette.

<newline>&empty;<newline>
<figure nonumber entity=ImageV-Pan-Tool>
<\figure>
<newline>&empty;<newline>

<item>Move the pointer into the View window, over the image or page.

<newline>&empty;
<p gentity=ImageV-Pan-Hand gposition=left>The pointer changes to a hand shape.
<newline>&empty;

<item>Drag the pointer in the direction you want to move the image or page.

<newline>&empty;
<!-- <figure nonumber entity=ImageV-Pan-Hand-Move> -->
<!-- <\figure> -->
<p gentity=ImageV-Pan-Hand-Move gposition=left>&empty;
<newline>&empty;

<item>Click the Pan tool to deselect it.
<\list>

